TaskFlowObject

public TaskFlowObject(java.lang.String fuseCardCode,
                      java.lang.String fuseObjectCode,
                      java.lang.String fuseTaskFlowParamList,
                      java.lang.String contextCode,
                      java.lang.String objectType,
                      java.lang.String objectName,
                      java.lang.String objectId,
                      java.lang.String webAppName,
                      java.lang.String viewId)
Constructs a TaskFlowObject for FUSE recent items with the specified parameters. The parameters fuseCardCode, fuseObjectCode and objectName are mandatory. If the mandatory values are not specified then the TaskFlowObject is not added to the FUSE recent items list.

Parameters:
fuseCardCode - fuse card code of the fuse object.
fuseObjectCode - object code of the fuse object
fuseTaskFlowParamList - parameters for the fuse card.
contextCode - contextCode of the fuse object
objectType - type or classification of the fuse object
objectName - displayName of the fuse object
objectId - unique identifier of the fuse object for a specific type
webAppName - deployedModuleName of the current WebApp
viewId - viewId of the current fuse card
